io.scanbot.hicscanner

Enum HealthInsuranceCardValidationType


  • public enum HealthInsuranceCardValidationType

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ValidationNone

        public static HealthInsuranceCardValidationType ValidationNone

        No content validation is performed.

      • ValidationAutoAny

        public static HealthInsuranceCardValidationType ValidationAutoAny

        The issuing country is inferred and the validation rules for that country are used. If the issuing country cannot be inferred, no content validation is performed.

      • ValidationAutoSupported

        public static HealthInsuranceCardValidationType ValidationAutoSupported

        The issuing country is inferred and the validation rules for that country are used. If the issuing country cannot be inferred, a validation failure error is returned.

      • ValidationGerman

        public static HealthInsuranceCardValidationType ValidationGerman

        The issuing country is assumed to be Germany. Validation on the personal identification number, and issuing institution number is performed as described in "Spezifikation f√ºr Musterkarten und Testkarten (eGK, HBA, SMC), Anhang A" and "GS1 Struktur der Kenn-Nummer (ICCSN) der elektronischen Gesundheitskarte"

      • ValidationAustrian

        public static HealthInsuranceCardValidationType ValidationAustrian

        The issuing country is assumed to be Austria. Validation on the personal identification number is performed as described in "site:www.sozialversicherung.at Was ist die Versicherungsnummer?"
